    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cylindrical or tapering graduated vessels calibrated in fluid ounces or milliliters for measuring the volume of liquids.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
